Package io.openems.edge.bridge.modbus.api

Class ElementToChannelConverter

java.lang.Object
io.openems.edge.bridge.modbus.api.ElementToChannelConverter
Direct Known Subclasses:
ElementToChannelConverterChain, ElementToChannelOffsetConverter, ElementToChannelScaleFactorConverter, IgnoreZeroConverter
public class ElementToChannelConverter extends Object
Provides Functions to convert from Element to Channel and back. Also has some static convenience functions to facilitate conversion.
